<div class="banner" style="background-image: asset-url('home/banner.jpg');">
  <div class="container">
    <h1><strong>S</strong>mith <strong>P</strong>aragliding <strong>S</strong>chool</h1>
    <p><span id="banner-typed-text"></span></p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <h2>You want to discover our sport ? </h2>
  <h2>Come with us soaring with the birds high above the charming Swiss village of Villars-Sur-Ollon.</h2>
  <h2>The professional pilots of Smith Paragliding can safely introduce you to the sky ! </h2>
  <h2>They are masters of all forms of foot launched flight and are recognized by the Swiss Federal Aviation Administration and Paragliding Federation</h2>
</div>

